Usage:
  mor [options] [PACKAGE...] bootstrap
  mor [options] [PACKAGE...] install [--save-dev | --save] [<package>...]
  mor [options] [PACKAGE...] run CMD
  mor [options] [PACKAGE...] exec CMD

Options:
  --dependents, -t 			dependents
  --transitive-dependendents, -T 	dependents, including transitive dependents
  --dependencies, -d    		dependencies
  --transitive-dependencies, -D    	dependencies, including transitive dependencies
